ted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E8%8C%83%E5%8D%9A--------/" target="_blank">范博</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/6/" target="_blank">动作片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.23</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>20世纪30年代，上海滩风云巨变日本人把东北毒气弹工厂位置隐藏于密电码之中，密电码得不到破译，东北民众生命安全将受到极大威胁。冯敬尧残忍杀害爱国人士抢走密电码，锄奸团为了救万民于水火必须将其夺回，彻底瓦解日本人的生化武器基地，于是在上海滩展开了一场血雨腥风的博弈。&nbsp;</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/99623/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/99496/" data-original="https://img.tupian-zuida.com/pic/upload/vod/2019-08-21/201908211566369484.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">10.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">20集全</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/99496/">上海滩续集国语</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%90%95%E8%89%AF%E4%BC%9F------------/" target="_blank">吕良伟</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%BB%84%E6%B7%91%E4%BB%AA------------/" target="_blank">黄淑仪</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%B0%A2%E8%B4%A4------------/" target="_blank">谢贤</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%BB%96%E5%90%AF%E6%99%BA------------/" target="_blank">廖启智</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E6%8B%9B%E6%8C%AF%E5%BC%BA--------/" target="_blank">招振强</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/14/" target="_blank">港台剧</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1980/" target="_blank">1980</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.22</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>《上海滩续集》(英文：The Bund II）是香港无线电视1980年乘接《上海滩》余威，再推出这部情节更扣人心弦、斗争更具爆炸性的《上海滩续集》，将民初上海的风云际会，帮会斗争，推至另一新高峰《上海滩续集》全剧共20集，监制招振强，主要演员有吕良伟、黄淑仪、谢贤、廖启智等。主题曲《万般情》由顾嘉辉</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/99496/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/98907/" data-original="https://img.tupian-zuida.com/pic/upload/vod/2019-08-18/201908181566105250.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">2.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">20集全</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/98907/">上海滩龙虎斗国语</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%90%95%E8%89%AF%E4%BC%9F------------/" target="_blank">吕良伟</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%AC%A7%E9%98%B3%E4%BD%A9%E7%8F%8A------------/" target="_blank">欧阳佩珊</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%BB%84%E5%85%83%E7%94%B3------------/" target="_blank">黄元申</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%94%98%E5%9B%BD%E5%8D%AB------------/" target="_blank">甘国卫</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%BB%84%E6%97%A5%E5%8D%8E------------/" target="_blank">黄日华</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%8B%97%E4%BE%A8%E4%BC%9F------------/" target="_blank">苗侨伟</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E9%82%B1%E5%AE%B6%E9%9B%84--------/" target="_blank">邱家雄</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/14/" target="_blank">港台剧</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1980/" target="_blank">1980</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.18</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>反映上海大亨，为巩固自已的势力，彼此勾心斗角的剧集．他们巧取豪夺，甚至要取对方的性命，在这种斗争中，牺牲了很多无辜者 才华出众的纪先勇（黄元申）大学毕业后，欲投靠丁力，没被接纳．于是他投靠了另一大亨厉峻，颇为厉峻赏识，生意十分蓬勃．但厉峻为人阴险手辣，利用纪先勇扩张势力．而纪先勇的女朋友叶秋盈（欧阳</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/98907/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/51871/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2018-12-23/201812231545532622.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">1.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/51871/">赌侠2：上海滩赌圣</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%91%A8%E6%98%9F%E9%A9%B0------------/" target="_blank">周星驰</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%B7%A9%E4%BF%90------------/" target="_blank">巩俐</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%90%95%E8%89%AF%E4%BC%9F------------/" target="_blank">吕良伟</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%90%91%E5%8D%8E%E5%BC%BA------------/" target="_blank">向华强</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E7%8E%8B%E6%99%B6--------/" target="_blank">王晶</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-------------/" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/7/" target="_blank">喜剧片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1991/" target="_blank">1991</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.05</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>阿星（周星驰 饰）由赌神处学成归来，恰逢不甘心失败的大军集合中南海五大高手复仇，虽有龙五（向华强 饰）相助，但阿星与三叔（吴孟达 饰）仍被大军等人发功送至1937年的上海……阿星与三叔失散后意外击杀谋害许文强之凶手，得以结识丁力（吕良伟 饰），自此与祖父周大福（吴孟达 饰）留在丁力身边，丁力女友如仙</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/51871/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/59182/" data-original="http://pic.youku778.com/upload/vod/2019-06-29/15617702161.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">9.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">高清1080p</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/59182/">马永贞决战上海滩</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%88%98%E5%B1%B9%E5%AE%B8------------/" target="_blank">刘屹宸</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%82%AC%E9%9D%96%E9%9D%96------------/" target="_blank">邬靖靖</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%AE%B8%E8%AF%97%E6%99%A8------------/" target="_blank">许诗晨</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%96%BB%E4%BA%A2--------/" target="_blank">喻亢</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/6/" target="_blank">动作片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2019/" target="_blank">2019</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>影片讲述了清末民初的旧上海，列强侵略，纷争不断面对这样的危急形势，震东帮帮主马永贞和他的恩师“码头之王”谭四爷小心应对。不料东洋人为达到运输鸦片入沪的目的将谭四爷残忍暗杀，并且将马永贞未婚妻虐待致死，在这样国仇家恨齐来、命悬一线的危急时刻，马永贞带领部下奋起反抗，激起上海滩无数浪花……</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/59182/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/83422/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-05-25/201905251558762807.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">7.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">25集全/已完结</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/83422/">上海滩</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%91%A8%E6%B6%A6%E5%8F%91------------/" target="_blank">周润发</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%B5%B5%E9%9B%85%E8%8A%9D------------/" target="_blank">赵雅芝</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%90%95%E8%89%AF%E4%BC%9F------------/" target="_blank">吕良伟</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%88%98%E4%B8%B9------------/" target="_blank">刘丹</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%B1%A4%E9%95%87%E4%B8%9A------------/" target="_blank">汤镇业</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9E%97%E5%BB%BA%E6%98%8E------------/" target="_blank">林建明</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%BB%96%E5%90%AF%E6%99%BA------------/" target="_blank">廖启智</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9B%E9%9F%B3------------/" target="_blank">景黛音</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%99%88%E7%AB%8B%E5%93%81------------/" target="_blank">陈立品</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E6%8B%9B%E6%8C%AF%E5%BC%BA--------/" target="_blank">招振强</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/14/" target="_blank">港台剧</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1980/" target="_blank">1980</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>上海滩上龙争虎斗，仇杀漫天大学生许文强（周润发 饰）经历过失败的学生运动后，只身来到上海，他与小贩丁力（吕良伟 饰）成为至交，并在同学方艳云的帮助下，混入黑帮，并凭借自己的勇谋成为帮派头目。上海法租界大亨冯敬尧看中许文强的才干，想招其至门下，被文强婉言谢绝。许文强偶然救了冯敬尧之女冯程程（赵雅芝 饰</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/83422/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/77787/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-03-08/201903081551988677.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">5.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/77787/">铁蛋勇闯上海滩</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E8%8C%83%E5%A4%A7%E6%AF%9B------------/" target="_blank">范大毛</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%8C%83%E4%BA%8C%E6%AF%9B------------/" target="_blank">范二毛</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%8E%8B%E4%BC%9F------------/" target="_blank">王伟</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9D%8E%E8%89%B3%E5%86%B0------------/" target="_blank">李艳冰</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E8%83%A1%E5%AE%97%E7%A5%A5--------/" target="_blank">胡宗祥</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/7/" target="_blank">喜剧片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2016/" target="_blank">2016</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>铁蛋的媳妇二妞被发廊土豪一线天抢走！为夺回老婆，铁蛋踏上寻妻之路，远征上海滩铁蛋必须大战浦口码头斧头帮，对决静安寺按摩院香艳春丽，斗舞人民广场灭绝师太，登陆硝烟弥漫的八仙桥菜市沙场，拜访精武门陈真以茶代酒唠家常，最后杀入和平饭店大乱战。功夫杀敌不困难，但铁蛋应该如何赢回二妞飘走的心？</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/77787/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/63872/" data-original="https://img.tupian-zuida.com/pic/upload/vod/2019-02-21/201902211550725791.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">10.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">25集全</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/63872/">上海滩国语</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%91%A8%E6%B6%A6%E5%8F%91------------/" target="_blank">周润发</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%B5%B5%E9%9B%85%E8%8A%9D------------/" target="_blank">赵雅芝</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%90%95%E8%89%AF%E4%BC%9F------------/" target="_blank">吕良伟</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%88%98%E4%B8%B9------------/" target="_blank">刘丹</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E6%8B%9B%E6%8C%AF%E5%BC%BA--------/" target="_blank">招振强</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/14/" target="_blank">港台剧</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1980/" target="_blank">1980</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>上海滩上龙争虎斗，仇杀漫天大学生许文强（周润发 饰）经历过失败的学生运动后，只身来到上海，他与小贩丁力（吕良伟 饰）成为至交，并在同学方艳云的帮助下，混入黑帮，并凭借自己的勇谋成为帮派头目。上海法租界大亨冯敬尧看中许文强的才干，想招其至门下，被文强婉言谢绝。许文强偶然救了冯敬尧之女冯程程（赵雅芝 饰</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/63872/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/23765/" data-original="http://pic.iqiyi6123.com/upload/vod/2019-01-17/15477194777.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">4.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center"></span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/23765/">上海滩十三太保</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E7%8B%84%E9%BE%99------------/" target="_blank">狄龙</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%A7%9C%E5%A4%A7%E5%8D%AB------------/" target="_blank">姜大卫</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%A2%81%E5%AE%B6%E4%BB%81------------/" target="_blank">梁家仁</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%8E%8B%E7%BE%BD------------/" target="_blank">王羽</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%BC%A0%E5%BD%BB--------/" target="_blank">张彻</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/6/" target="_blank">动作片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE-----------/" target="_blank">台湾</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1984/" target="_blank">1984</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>抗日时期，爱国人士高先生不满汪伪政权卖国行径，与神偷黑帽子（王羽 饰）将双方密约窃走，计划将其公开上海富商沈刚夫（陈观泰 饰）受人所托，命上海滩十三太保保护高先生离沪赴港。南京方面内务部长官洪述亦同时动作，收买部分太保暗杀高先生……长枪小杨（李修贤 饰）首先发难行刺却因失手被洪述清除，高先生先后在烟</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/23765/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/67592/" data-original="https://img.tupian-zuida.com/pic/upload/vod/2019-06-30/201906301561897506.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">10.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">40集全</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/67592/">新上海滩国语</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E9%99%88%E9%94%A6%E9%B8%BF------------/" target="_blank">陈锦鸿</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%83%91%E5%B0%91%E7%A7%8B------------/" target="_blank">郑少秋</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%99%88%E6%9D%BE%E4%BC%B6------------/" target="_blank">陈松伶</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9E%97%E5%AE%B6%E6%A0%8B------------/" target="_blank">林家栋</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%BC%A0%E5%8F%AF%E9%A2%90------------/" target="_blank">张可颐</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%A2%81%E5%B0%8F%E5%86%B0------------/" target="_blank">梁小冰</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%83%91%E8%A3%95%E7%8E%B2------------/" target="_blank">郑裕玲</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9E%97%E4%BF%9D%E6%80%A1------------/" target="_blank">林保怡</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%83%AD%E5%B0%91%E8%8A%B8------------/" target="_blank">郭少芸</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%B0%AD%E8%80%80%E6%96%87------------/" target="_blank">谭耀文</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%BD%97%E5%98%89%E8%89%AF------------/" target="_blank">罗嘉良</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E4%BC%9F------------/" target="_blank">曾志伟</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%85%B3%E5%AE%9D%E6%85%A7------------/" target="_blank">关宝慧</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%BD%97%E5%AE%B6%E8%8B%B1------------/" target="_blank">罗家英</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E4%BD%95%E7%BE%8E%E9%92%BF------------/" target="_blank">何美钿</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E6%8B%9B%E9%9A%85%E6%A0%8B--------/" target="_blank">招隅栋</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/14/" target="_blank">港台剧</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1996/" target="_blank">1996</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>抗战期间，东北赌王于镇海（郑少秋 饰）为了帮助恩师夺回被上海流氓大亨冯敬尧（潘志文 饰）夺走的赌场百乐门，带着手下和恩师的儿子洛天佑来到了上海于镇海向冯敬尧下了赌桌挑战贴，筹码就是百乐门，冯敬尧虽然心知来着不善，但为了面子还是答应出战。一时上海黑白两道大为紧张，人人都争相想看这场被称为世纪赌局的赌坛</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/67592/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><div class="fed-page-info fed-text-center"><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info fed-hide fed-show-xs-inline fed-btns-disad" href="/s/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E6%BB%A9------------/">首页</a><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info fed-btns-disad" href="/s/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E6%BB%A9------------/">上页</a><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info fed-hide fed-show-sm-inline fed-btns-green" href="javascript:;">1</a><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info fed-hide fed-show-sm-inline" href="/s/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E6%BB%A9----------2---/">2</a><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info fed-